law.history: Repealed 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 476, sec. 32, effective January 1, 2001. -- Created 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 496, sec. 21, effective April 10, 1998.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Insurer annual reports -- Department calculations and notification to insurer -- Assessments and refunds -- Stop-loss carrier -- Examinations of participating insurers.
